 <div class="popover">
    <div class="popover--link">
        <span class="help-popover">
            <i class="material-icons">help</i>
        </span>
        <div class="popover--message popover--message--right">
            <h4>Page Url</h4>
            <p>The page url represents the name of your webpage in the address bar. An example would be if you used the name <span class="bold">"about"</span> your pages web address would be ( www.yoursite.com/about ). Page urls should be as small and unique as possible and use ('&ndash;') to separate words instead of spaces.</p>
            <div class="popover-footer--action">
                <a class="button button_app_color">Ok</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>